OL,4,Cover custody suite closures
OL,6,FThe Police Federation has expressed
OL,7,F'concern' for the safety of police
OL,8,Fofficers over custody suite closures.
OL,10,FThe union fears they have to travel
OL,11,Flong distances to custody suites
OL,12,Fbecause Enniskillen has been shut
OL,13,Fpermanently and Omagh is closed for 12
OL,14,Fmonths for refurbishment.
OL,16,FOfficers have told UTV it is taking
OL,17,Fvital resources away and adding to
OL,18,Fstress and pressure in the job.
