OL,6,FEnniskillen custody suite was closed
OL,7,Fin 2021 and the PSNI says there are no
OL,8,Fplans to reopen it.
OL,10,F''After careful and exhaustive
OL,11,Fconsideration of a range of factors
OL,12,Fincluding the standard of the custody
OL,13,Ffacilities, the level of demand, the
OL,14,Fneeds of the community and of
OL,15,Fdetainees," police said in a statement.
OL,17,F"The ongoing refurbishment work in
OL,18,FOmagh is part of our long term custody
OL,19,Fstrategy which aims to provide safe
OL,20,Fand accessible custody provision
OL,21,Facross the service."
