OL,6,FFermanagh solicitor Gary Black thinks
OL,7,FEnniskillen can't understand why it
OL,8,Fwas closed in the first place and
OL,9,Fwants to see it reopen.
OL,11,F"You could have four persons arrested
OL,12,Fand all of a sudden you have four
OL,13,Fvehicles and eight officers on route
OL,14,Fto custody now in Strabane and that
OL,15,Fcertainly has lead to more officers
OL,16,Foff the ground."
