OL,3,CConcern over officer safety because
OL,4,Cover custody suite closures
OL,6,FIn a statement the PFNI said: "Our
OL,7,Fconcern is the potential risk to
OL,8,Fofficers who have to spent longer
OL,9,Fperiods in vehicles transporting
OL,10,Fdetained and occasionally violent
OL,11,Findividuals.
OL,13,F"Officers can be impacted by working
OL,14,Flonger hours if they need to interview
OL,15,Fand then return to their home station
OL,16,Fwhich may be 60 miles away at the end
OL,17,Fof their shift.
