OL,6,F"Nightshift would pose a particular
OL,7,Fsafety concern with the additional
OL,8,Ftravelling when tired.J"Travelling
OL,9,Flong distances also impacts on the
OL,10,Fresources available in the towns that
OL,11,FtheJofficers leave".
OL,13,FUlster Unionist Councillor Mark Owns
OL,14,Ftold UTV: "We are the biggest council
OL,15,Fin NI (by size) and it just strikes
OL,16,Fthat it's madness that there isn't a
OL,17,Fsingle custody suite in this entire
OL,18,Farea.
