OL,6,F"I wouldn't be surprised that officers
OL,7,Fare considering making fewer arrests
OL,8,Fbecause of the long distances they
OL,9,Fhave to travel. It's unfortunately
OL,10,Fperhaps one of the unintended
OL,11,Fconsequences of the decision close
OL,12,FEnniskillen and then subsequently to
OL,13,Ftemp close Omagh".
OL,15,FOver the past decade, 10 custody
OL,16,Fsuites have been closed across
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland.
