OL,6,FThe PSNI said: "There is no evidence
OL,7,Fthat fewer arrests in the Fermanagh
OL,8,Fand Omagh district are as a result of
OL,9,Fofficers travelling with detained
OL,10,Fpeople to custody.
OL,12,F"When responding to incidents police
OL,13,Fofficers must consider all of the
OL,14,Favailable criminal justice outcomes
OL,15,Fand disposals, including arrest,
OL,16,Fstreet bail, community resolution
OL,17,Fnotices and cautions".
